{"tid":807443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰】美國蘋果農憂高關稅 做好準備大幅降價","createTime":"2018-09-05T13:37:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T02:11:01.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59278bccbf09da7b8aa909a59322b9ce8bd39bcd","tid":807443,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T13:37:05.000Z","msg":"【貿易戰】美國蘋果農憂高關稅 做好準備大幅降價<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180905&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58646817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180905%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58646817&d=sjKPZasU5IfbdY%2BdwfgagpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=186f3dec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180905%26s%3D7015342%26a%3D58646817&h=ad7b4d9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180905&amp;s=7015342&amp;a=58646817</a><br />\n<br />\n美國擬向中國2,000億美元商品徵收關稅，公眾諮詢將於明日美國時間結束，《路透社》引述美國蘋果果農表示，擔心會步當地車厘子果農後塵，將做好降價的準備。<br />\n<br />\n位於華盛頓州的車厘子和蘋果種植商奧威爾水果公司銷售市場主管Ray Norwood稱，面對貿易戰，他們希望很快可以得到解決，但情況不明朗，故只能撐著，並指車厘子生產商出口的車厘子在中國港口被扣留，最後被收取高關稅，對該公司的利潤造成很大影響。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">他指出中國是其第三大出口市場，約80%車厘子銷往中國，但最終只能降低售價和尋找其他目的地。此外，蘋果銷售商同樣做好降價的準備，華盛頓蘋果委員會的國際市場主管Rebecca Lyons說，因為中國向美國蘋果徵收了高達50%的關稅，故料蘋果會大幅降價。<br />\n</span><br />\n據華盛頓蘋果委員會指出，蘋果是華盛頓州產量最大的農產品，每年銷量約有20億至25億美元，約有三成用於出口。"},{"pid":"b9e40c5e262e46d93ad1ced808d8b3cdac326dbf","tid":807443,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"有平靚正美國蘋果食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7503939cc36b1fa236b130a8e33cc11f7deb0575","tid":807443,"uid":78791,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T13:41:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac8038694c5c4bc816deaaf9aa3f9c5b66d08107","tid":807443,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9e40c5e262e46d93ad1ced808d8b3cdac326dbf","tid":807443,"uid":54733,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T13:38:41.000Z","msg":"有平靚正美國蘋果食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T13:42:28.000Z","msg":"食完平車雁子，又有大量蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6ab1c17e397f6f92a496df2dfe1d098e22f9da","tid":807443,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T01:56:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74fa4cbaf0188ec3513c2648a0399ec45ccbfff8","tid":807443,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T02:11:01.000Z","msg":"香港成為最大贏家"}]}